Creates a new `Duration` from the specified number of microseconds.

# Examples

```
use std::time::Duration;

let duration = Duration::from_micros(1_000_002);

assert_eq!(1, duration.as_secs());
assert_eq!(2_000, duration.subsec_nanos());
```
